<DocsPageTitle>
    Badge component
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    The <Code Tag>Badge</Code> component is used to convey small pieces of information. Using the <Code>CloseClicked</Code> property,
    the chip becomes interactive, allowing user interaction.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Examples
</DocsPageSubtitle>

